6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to revenue and taxation; amending
Section 8, Chapter 354, O.S.L. 2022 (68 O.S. Supp.
8 2025, Section 3937), which relates to certain tax
credits; modifying date with respect to applications
9 for credits; and providing an effective date.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 8, Chapter 354, O.S.L.
14 2022 (68 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 3937), is amended to read as
15 follows:
16 Section 3937. The Department shall accept no new applications
17 for tax credits authorized under this act after December 1, 2032
18 2026.
19 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
